title: Failed Test Results
description: When a test failure occurs, it is associated with a failure reason. To help you  monitor the quality of a Project via test failures, TestOps comes with a Failed Test Results chart that organizes test failures by reason type.Attention: Failed Test Results  is limited to the Premium     and Ultimate  plans of Katalon Platform. See Katalon Platform plans for more information.
